Lingua-Tolkien-BURL version 0.01
================================

Garn lab bûnur srinukh, bag dalug-hai shâtaza!

BURL - an Orkish filter for Perl.

This module requires no c compiler.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Filter::Simple

